load ../infoflow-field-signature.maude

--- Per-field flow signature soundness. A tool result field carries only the reads
--- reaching it, at fact granularity, with the rule-level opaque box preserved. The
--- coverage searches show the per-field reach never under-reports a real leak; the
--- bite searches show the refinement is real -- a field independent of a
--- confidential read does not carry it.

--- ============================ COVERAGE, leak reachable =====================

--- Coverage: a field whose ROOT is a direct binding of a confidential fact chain
--- a tr root of fA with factReach fA hi carries that read, so releasing to a public sink
--- leaks. Per-field precision does NOT drop a read the field truly depends on.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-FIELD-SIGNATURE :
  own(lo) factReach(fA, hi) factReach(fB, lo)
  field(tr(fA) . nilR) sink(lo)
  =>* C:Cfg leak .

--- Coverage: a field with a DERIVED root dv has opaque provenance, so it falls
--- back to the whole-result reach. With some confidential fact chain present it is
--- hi, so releasing to a public sink leaks -- the fail-closed conservative fallback.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-FIELD-SIGNATURE :
  own(lo) factReach(fA, lo) factReach(fB, hi)
  field(dv . nilR) sink(lo)
  =>* C:Cfg leak .

--- Coverage: own-reads reach EVERY field -- the opaque box I-IFC2. Even a field
--- whose only root is a public fact chain leaks when the completing rule own-reads
--- are confidential -- the per-field refinement never drops the rule own-reads.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-FIELD-SIGNATURE :
  own(hi) factReach(fA, lo) factReach(fB, lo)
  field(tr(fA) . nilR) sink(lo)
  =>* C:Cfg leak .

--- ============================ BITE, no leak ================================

--- Bite, THE point of per-field: a field whose roots are ALL traceable to public
--- fact chains does NOT carry an unrelated confidential read. fB is confidential but
--- unreferenced, own-reads are public -- releasing a tr root of fA to a public sink does NOT
--- leak, though the whole-result reach would. No solution.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-FIELD-SIGNATURE :
  own(lo) factReach(fA, lo) factReach(fB, hi)
  field(tr(fA) . nilR) sink(lo)
  =>* leak RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: a cleared hi audience may receive a confidential field. The field reach
--- is hi but the sink is hi, so no leak. No solution.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-FIELD-SIGNATURE :
  own(lo) factReach(fA, hi) factReach(fB, lo)
  field(tr(fA) . nilR) sink(hi)
  =>* leak RESIDUAL:Cfg .
